data.text:
What is the meaning of the name Quetzal?

The name Quetzal is primarily a female name of Aztec origin that means Precious Flower, Queen.

Short form of the name Quetzalxochitl.

People who like the name Quetzal also like:

Quetzalxochitl, Zyanya, Xochitl, Zaniyah, Luna, Leilani, Amara, Atticus, Apollo, Dante, Roberto, Sebastian, Oliver, Heath
